OL,3,CChild dies after suspected dog bite
OL,5,FA child has died following a suspected
OL,6,Fdog bite, according to Cleveland
OL,7,FPolice.
OL,9,FOfficers were called to a property on
OL,10,FHardale Drive, in the Dormanstown area
OL,11,Fof Redcar, shortly after 1.30pm on
OL,12,FThursday afternoon, where they found
OL,13,Fthe child had died.
OL,15,FArmed officers destroyed one dog on
OL,16,Fthe street, while another was removed
OL,17,Ffrom the property.
OL,19,FPolice said there is "a scene in place
OL,20,Fat the address" as they investigate
OL,21,Fthe child's death.
