OL,3,CChild dies after suspected dog bite
OL,5,FCleveland Police said: "Understandably
OL,6,Fthis is a distressing and tragic
OL,7,Fincident, and our thoughts are with
OL,8,Fthe child's family."
OL,10,FOfficers are urging anyone with
OL,11,Finformation to get in touch.
OL,13,FA North East Ambulance Service
OL,14,Fspokesperson said: "We were called to
OL,15,Fan incident at a private address in
OL,16,FRedcar on Thursday April 9 shortly
OL,17,Fbefore 1.30pm.
OL,19,F"We dispatched three ambulance crews,
OL,20,Fone clinical team leader and one duty
OL,21,Fofficer to the incident.
